    "translation":{"eng":"If one obtains even a momentary vision of You, then all sorts of terrible miseries disappear, and one’s gross and subtle bodies are easily destroyed. Bhaktivinoda says, “All glories, all glories to the holy names of Śrī Hari! I prostrate myself in hopes of attaining Your lotus feet.”"}}
